Daily Mass

Monday, Wednesday and Friday - 8 AM

Tuesday and Thursday - 12:10 PM

(Church is open @1/2 hour prior to mass times only.)

Saturday 4:00 PM (Vigil Mass)

Sunday 8 AM and 11:00 AM (Church is open @ 45 minutes prior to Mass times only.)

HOLYDAY of OBLIGATION: Friday, November 1, Solemnity of All Saints

Friday, November 1, 2024 is the Solemnity of All Saints, a Holy day of obligation. Mass times that day only are 8:00 am and 12:10 pm

Confessions

Saturday 3:00 - 3:45 PM and by appointment

Please note that there is additional parking available nearbyour main church lot...

If the paved church parking lot is full, drive to 6th Ave South and enter the grass lot just south of the church, on the north side of the Avenue. Please only park on the grass - not on the gravel. We have special permission from the Hospital to use the grass , but they need the gravel area for their valet parking. Do not enter this lot from the alleyway - only from 6th Ave S.

Please note that this lot is available for all liturgies and special events at Saint Mary's.
